{"tid":803414,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"End clothing 入黎團購慳運費 每單$20","createTime":"2018-09-02T09:10:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T15:46:36.000Z","uid":92659,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3419262cffed37f863ef5a677d5d16eb912aa90e","tid":803414,"uid":92659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:10:19.000Z","msg":"產品link<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.endclothing.com/hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.endclothing.com%2Fhk&d=ZlKfbH7KqDG2KqnAb5yh1v755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=e438767d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.endclothing.com/hk</a><br />\n<br />\n小弟係觀塘有個地方可以幫大家團購。今次開團只係想儲下客底。真心以最平價錢幫大家。每單只係一次性+$20運費，10人成團。到左貨可以約時間上黎拎，取貨十分彈性。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果大家有興趣就係呢張google form留資料啦。成團會通知大家。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.goo.gl/ESq4FT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.goo.gl%2FESq4FT&d=ZlKfbH7KqDG2KqnAb5yh1v755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=cad8c3e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.goo.gl/ESq4FT</a><br />\n<br />\n如果大家鐘意小弟ge團購，敬請follow我IG la.<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/buyumore\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fbuyumore&d=ZlKfbH7KqDG2KqnAb5yh1v755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=ad16489d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.instagram.com/buyumore</a>"},{"pid":"c8c6a85c39a6ed4eda269a106867d7ee6bac50df","tid":803414,"uid":10340,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:18:31.000Z","msg":"上得endclothing買野仲慳住個180運費去集運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8465e988475d95ab7ed2f5187dda7a077703aa72","tid":803414,"uid":92659,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"c8c6a85c39a6ed4eda269a106867d7ee6bac50df","tid":803414,"uid":10340,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:18:31.000Z","msg":"上得endclothing買野仲慳住個180運費去集運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" cla